casebody.data:
Thursday, April 23, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

98-68. State ex rel. Nix v. Cleveland.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of respondents’ motion to quash subpoena,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to quash subpoena be, and hereby is, granted.

Pfeifer, J., dissents.
